HB 510 Original 2026 Regular Session Schamerhorn
Abstract: Requires that carbon dioxide for sequestration in La. be generated within the
state.
Present law (R.S. 30:1104(C)) provides for one of the conditions in an enumerated list of
conditions to be met prior to the use of any reservoir for storage and the exercise of eminent
domain for a reservoir for storage.
Proposed law requires that each of the enumerated conditions be met prior to the use of any
reservoir for storage and the exercise of eminent domain for a reservoir for storage.
Proposed law adds a provision to the list of enumerated conditions in present law that the
carbon dioxide to be stored be produced within the state of La.
(Amends R.S. 30:1104(C)(intro. para.); Adds R.S. 30:1104(C)(4))
